HEADWORD: Polygenism
<hw>Po*lyg"e*nism</hw> <pr>(p⟦osl⟧*l⟦icr⟧j"⟦esl⟧*n⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>polyg⟦eacute⟧nisme</ets>.]</ety>
